- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possibility as the paper mentions node classification and recommendation, which are common tasks in information retrieval.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper deals with machine learning and network representation, which are common topics in AI research.
- cs.DB (Databases) is also a possibility as the paper deals with heterogeneous networks and network embedding, which are relevant to database research.
